<title>ạ̉nạ qlby mryḍ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- dạkẖlyn qdạmk bnṣly wạ̹nt ạlṭlbạt
 bnsbḥ ạsmk wnʿly lyk ạ̉gẖnyạt
 nḥky ʿnk fy wsṭynạ ʿn ʿmlk ạlṣạlḥ fynạ
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉nạ qlby mryḍ bḥb yswʿ
 wdwạyạ ạ̉kyd qrbk yạ yswʿ
 2- qlby mftwn bjmạl ḥbk mạbysẖbʿ byk
 mhmạ ạ̉bqy̱ mʿạk wbqrbk ạ̉sẖtạq tạny lyk
 wdwạyạ sẖmạlk tʿạnqny wymynk fwq tḥạwṭny
 3- fy ʿyny qsẖwr ạksẖfhạly ạ̉nạ ṭlby ạ̉rạk
 fy ạlʿmq mʿạk ạnzʿhạly ạ̉nạ hạstnạk
 wạ̹n ṭạl ạlwqt lsẖfạỷy ḥbk mrḍy whw dwạỷy</lyrics>
</song>